title: 11/24/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 11/24/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Brady Quinn about the new College Football Playoff rankings. What are the chances that Cincy can still fall off? Caller Doug in North Carolina has a controversial take about food touching each other on a plate. And The Office's Brian Baumgartner joins DP to discuss his new book on the hit television show.
